name: Invesco Canadian Core Plus Bond ETF
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objectives, Invesco Canadian Core Plus Bond ETF invests primarily in debt securities that are rated investment grade. The portfolio management team carries out in-depth research to look for debt securities across various maturities whose fundamental values are not reflected in their credit ratings and prices, and which offer attractive opportunities relative to risk. There is no attempt to mirror the composition of the Invesco Canadian Core Plus Bond ETFs benchmark bond index. The investments are mainly in Canadian dollar-denominated securities.
